            "id": "4807431"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股半日升0.92%",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;     日经平均指数半日收报50,610.04点，升461.22点或0.92%。 (ST)</span>\n</div>",
